OL,3,CRAF veteran, 88, says new life as
OL,4,Cfoster carer helps him 'stay young'
OL,6,FA former jet fighter pilot has spoken
OL,7,Fabout his new life as a foster carer
OL,8,Fat the age of 88.
OL,10,FRAF veteran Nigel, whose surname has
OL,11,Fnot been given, said he took up
OL,12,Ffostering with Somerset Council four
OL,13,Fyears ago following the death of his
OL,14,Fwife.
OL,16,FThe octogenarian who lives in Somerset
OL,17,Fsaid he had wanted to do something
OL,18,F"worthwhile" and "stay young"
