OL,3,CRAF veteran, 88, says new life as
OL,4,Cfoster carer helps him 'stay young'
OL,6,FOnce qualified, Nigel defied the odds
OL,7,Fand took a less traditional path to
OL,8,Fbecome the British fighter jet pilot
OL,9,Fhe had aspired to be, having initially
OL,10,Fbeen told there would be no further
OL,11,Fopportunities to train on the single-
OL,12,Fseat jets.
OL,14,FNigel says he now enjoys life's
OL,15,Fsmaller moments as a carer.
OL,17,F"My foster son and I both like cars
OL,18,Fand I still like fast things. We went
OL,19,Fgo-karting at Haynes Motor Museum a
OL,20,Fwhile ago which was fun," he said.
