OL,3,CRAF veteran, 88, says new life as
OL,4,Cfoster carer helps him 'stay young'
OL,6,F"One of my favourite memories with my
OL,7,Ffoster son was standing at the front
OL,8,Fof the Pyramid Stage watching Coldplay
OL,9,Fheadline Glastonbury Festival this
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,F"Stewards helped us make it to the
OL,13,Ffront where my daughter had been
OL,14,Fwaiting all day, so we were all there
OL,15,Ftogether.
OL,17,F"It was absolutely fantastic, the best
OL,18,Fthing they've ever done there, and my
OL,19,Ffoster son loved it too."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
