OL,3,CRAF veteran, 88, says new life as
OL,4,Cfoster carer helps him 'stay young'
OL,6,FNigel was worried about the
OL,7,Farrangement of fostering teens as an
OL,8,Folder man- but says it's worked out
OL,9,Fwell.
OL,11,F"I could well understand if he'd said,
OL,12,F'You've got to be joking'. But I am so
OL,13,Fglad it worked out because he is a
OL,14,Fwonderful kid. Wonderful.
OL,16,F"Being retired, I have 24 hours a day
OL,17,FI can devote to this child, and I have
OL,18,Fgrown-up children and grandchildren
OL,19,Fwho are all really supportive."
OL,26,@xD@AOU
