OL,3,CRAF veteran, 88, says new life as
OL,4,Cfoster carer helps him 'stay young'
OL,6,FCouncillor Heather Shearer, lead
OL,7,Fmember for children, families and
OL,8,Feducation at Somerset Council, added:
OL,9,F"As we approach Remembrance Day, I'd
OL,10,Fvery much like to thank Nigel for the
OL,11,Fmany ways he has and continues to
OL,12,Fdedicate his life to others, as an RAF
OL,13,Fveteran and as a foster carer.
OL,15,F"We absolutely need more people like
OL,16,FNigel to provide nurturing homes for
OL,17,Flocal children, where they too can be
OL,18,Finspired to achieve their dreams."
